
arrows	mouse movement
ESC	abort
SHIFT	OR blocking
CTRL	XOR blocking
RETURN	execute (geniusmove family)
	recalllastdata (geniusmove family)
TAB	cycle menu options

A,A	animate
A,B	beats
A,D	deanimate points
A,P	animate points
C,A	add to section
C,C	create collection
C,D	delete from section
C,E	edit section
C,R	remove collection
C,S	subtract collections
C,U	union collections
E,E	edit continuity instructions
E,G	gridsize
E,K	kill changes
E,U	undo
F,L	load show
F,M	merge shows
F,P	print show
F,Q	quit
F,S	save show
G,A	associate groups
G,C	create group
G,D	delete point
G,E	edit points
G,R	remove groups
G,S	select group
I	insert stuntsheet
L,A	relabel
L,D	down label
L,H	horizontal label flip
L,L	left label
L,N	name label
L,R	right label
L,U	up label
L,V	vertical label flip
M,C	clevermove
M,D	dilation
M,G	geniusmove
M,M	smartmove
M,R	rotation
M,S	shear
M,T	translation
M,X	reflection
N	next stuntsheet
P	previous stuntsheet
R,A	associate refpt sheets
R,C	copy refpt sheet
R,N	name refpt sheet
R,R	remove refpt sheet
R,S	select refpt sheet
R,U	autoname refpt sheets
S	stuntsheet
T	repeat last action
U	undo last action
Y,B	backslash inversion
Y,C	change symbol
Y,O	solid inversion
Y,S	slash inversion

animation control keys

arrows	manually animate
+	forward
-	backward
1-9	speed
A	automatic animation
B	bell on/off
C	collisions
H	highlight
S	type bpm
T	collision tolerance

stuntsheet control keys

A	autoname stuntsheets
C	copy stuntsheets
E	rename stuntsheet
G	goto stuntsheet
I	insert stuntsheet
M	move stuntsheets
N	next stuntsheet
P	previous stuntsheet
R	remove stuntsheets
U	undo

Commands for which it might be nice to have single keystroke keyboard
commands to speed usage.

